metadata.name: The King & His Army
metadata.description:
The King & His Army
2880x 2880x

A devout religious king led his army on a journey to spread their faith and conquer new lands. The king believed that their god had called upon him to expand their kingdom and spread their religion to the surrounding regions. He and his army were determined to follow their spiritual leader and fulfill their religious duties, even if it meant facing great challenges and sacrifices along the way. The king's unwavering faith and the loyalty of his army made them a formidable force, and they were able to achieve many victories during their journey.
